OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMist and fog locally lingering
OL,6,Funtil late morning. Otherwise, a dry
OL,7,Fday with an increasing amount of
OL,8,Fpleasant spring sunshine developing.
OL,9,FFeeling mild with a gentle breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry this evening and
OL,12,Fovernight with prolonged clear spells
OL,13,Ffor most. Patchy mist and fog
OL,14,Freforming, though more isolated than
OL,15,Fthe previous night. Chilly,
OL,16,Fparticularly for rural areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
