OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright start to Thursday
OL,6,Fas fog clears. Sunshine turning hazier
OL,7,Fin the afternoon ahead of rain
OL,8,Farriving later. Another very mild day
OL,9,Fbefore this.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:
OL,12,FTemperatures dropping nearer to
OL,13,Faverage to end the week. Some bright
OL,14,For sunny spells on Friday and
OL,15,FSaturday, but cloud generally building
OL,16,Finto the weekend with patchy rain
OL,17,Fpossible Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
